「Out of Tokyo」是王萌+于淼的音乐作品 视觉是在一次有关森山大道的展览开幕演出中
创作的致敬森山大道的视觉作品。 取材用理光相机拍摄Google地球上的日本街景，
演出现场配合音乐加入实时的特效处理。

-


“Out of Tokyo" is the music work of 
Wang Meng + Yu Miao. The visual is in the opening performance of an exhibition on Moriyama Avenue
A visual work created to pay tribute to Moriyama Avenue. I used a Ricoh camera to take pictures of Japanese street scenes on Google Earth,
Real-time special effects processing is added to the performance scene with music.


-

parcel.description:
A/V GALLERY is the virtual gallery of Atomic Visual Studio, built on blockchain-based online community. As new media art group and art curator, Atomic Visual will distribute A/V original NFT artworks, as well as other NFT artworks in the form of mix-media/ audio-visual/ illustration/ music etc. by our cooperative artists.

A/V GALLERY是放射能创立的虚拟艺术馆。放射能以新媒体艺术创作团体及策展人的身份，发行由放射能原创的NFT艺术作品，以及合作艺术家的NFT艺术作品，包括但不限于混合媒介、音视觉、插画、音乐等形式。
